<TITLE> Wachovia's shares fall 55 percent </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 NEW YORK, Mon Sep 29, (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Shares of Wachovia Corp fell 55 percent to $4.50 in trading before the opening bell on Monday. Wachovia is in talks with rivals to be taken over, sources familiar with the situation said on Sunday, after the US bank's shares fell 27 percent on Friday due to concerns about its portfolio of illiquid assets
